{"id":28305,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":24}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"问答栏:,大众信箱","genre":"","count":"75","ytitle":"","mtitle":"水冲掉的","ftitle":"","authors":["萼梅"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:看这个日本伤兵腿也没有，大概是华军的炸弹炸掉它的?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:不，是水冲掉的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:水能冲掉腿吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:因为日本人的腿是泥做的。"}]}